<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200915/de358082e3a24ca5a9d8a92e09519581.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200915/2245c19c323244aca2e6e5a6e11cd494.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>看到玛莎拉蒂的第一眼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>估计你也会和我一样会感叹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这腿真白</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这车真腿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>对不起……我想说的是</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这车真白</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200915/898cc799f5234f36ac8f1929e1b14160.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200915/6a6ba4213486466ba8e033abc720e289.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>对我而言</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>玛莎拉蒂Ghibli比奔驰CLS、奥迪A7更有格调</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>它能够将优雅和激情融为一体</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不同于德系干净利索、有棱有角</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>意大利设计师把它的性感</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>通过曲线来表达出来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>犹如少女曼妙的身姿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就算是不懂车的路人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>也能看出它独树一帜的气质</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200915/e87dba5a69c34261b9ff73395cd8c3cd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200915/6978fb11548342d2bb81362fed41baf6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200915/78e3c843f42647f8a4ef2e8038d62397.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200915/16a524dbf47641dbb5af1210371cb27c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我们可以负责地告诉大家</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Ghibli是大家最容易接触到的玛莎拉蒂</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>谈何容易？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一是因为它78.88-96.22万的价格</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>是玛莎拉蒂最便宜的车型</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>二是因为你可以在《和平精英》手游里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>运气好的话，花6块钱就能抽到一台</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>运气不好的话，花2000你也抽不出来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200915/f6e657b718f84c699ccf3cbed55f315c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Ghibli寓意为撒哈拉沙漠的热风</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>光是这个名字就足够有异域色彩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>标志性的鲨鱼嘴造型</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>硕大的三叉戟熠熠生辉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这就是“海王”最大的魅力</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200915/df2160a6a3934dfaa96ecae582b3b298.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200915/2a876b23477c436aae0e09e23e253945.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>矩阵式全LED大灯带有自适应功能</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>相比传统的卤素灯</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>要高出200%的照明宽度</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>以及55米的道路照明延伸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>寿命也是一般灯泡的两倍</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>用一句话总结就是：</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你看这个光，它又长又宽……</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200915/c4d3a34d22dc4056b7d0b8d0add3fcc0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200915/312e48ab48044ff9af75522e7963b130.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200915/d3134719469b488fb0d65bc4fce9281c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>三孔鲨鱼腮造型暗示着它的出色性能</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这也是玛莎拉蒂的家族化特征之一</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就算装饰作用大于实际功能</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>但谁又不喜欢让人血脉偾张的视觉元素呢？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200915/67aad70af9224f23b8f07ae25c915eec.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200915/f9e0b0aac654433590d4cbcf51a97935.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200915/fca9ee2114b148c686102ec353feadeb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200915/59e950a204554177838487cbc13eb2e7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Ghibli最好看的部位</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>当属尾部的线条</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>仿佛能看到1966年初代Ghibli的影子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>当年的Ghibli出自传奇设计师乔治·亚罗之手</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>大师的代表作各个都是汽车史上的经典，就包括</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>第一代高尔夫、法拉利250GT、阿尔法·罗密欧Giulia GT、</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>宝马3200CS、阿斯顿·马丁DB4等等</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200915/84004fae72cf42a78802648f4bfdbdb2.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200915/75865f93905a45438ecfb97a023d8743.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>细心的客官老爷可能留意到了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>拍摄现场天公不作美</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不过雨过天晴后</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>性感的外观映在水面的画板上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>气质依然优雅</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200915/23456985837d40f8813f12783d11b4f8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200915/9794f1fcdeb34d66b386902b9283b8a0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>私认为</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>没有无框车门的轿跑，都是假轿跑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你想想</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>打开车门，无框车门成为风景线</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>轻关车门，电吸功能让下车动作锦上添花</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这就是优雅</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200915/8bb2ee5a8f0f4f57a15474def8cdc954.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200915/3dc97d101312480bbf4be96a09146a6c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>粗犷的内饰设计和优雅的外观有些跳跃</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不过大面积的上乘小牛皮和实木饰板</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>加上车顶还全都是Alcantara材质包裹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>营造出很直接的豪华感</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我好像理解了女士们口中所说的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“包治百病”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200915/9fd77a3250d64756bdab49900735ce84.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200915/3d6dc5026cb045cb9f8638f79b373cce.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200915/19ed042ff1d147709fc85c567d2ac294.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>法国设计师总喜欢在汽车设计上搞点幺蛾子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>比如：</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>档把造型的喇叭，中间不转动的方向盘，还有曲面玻璃……</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还好意大利的设计师没有太浪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>左侧的启动按键、拨片的位置设置多媒体控制键</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这跟法系车的脑洞设计比起来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>真的是小巫见大巫了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200915/14b99170ed5b4b2ba6c3c31fd5b51f1e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200915/bf78f0a1723449c3a7b0618464ce0755.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200915/c04f881b4cf64226aa81cc60a40de16b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这个价位的车型，配置基本都是到顶的水平</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>选装了15个扬声器的宝华韦建音响</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>来一首《Por una cabeza》再合适不过</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>通过歌曲神游到电影里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200915/31a41cac54554a59bf1796c5d82b7fa3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200915/f1896c47dd19457db3c637c2ec6d3b54.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>8.4英寸的彩色触控屏功能非常全面</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>如果分辨率能再高一点</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我铁买（手动狗头）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200915/ea688685316b42fc8dd825e9f6cf7ea1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200915/ba50764fbeb2460db530284eb30c334c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>对于身材娇小的女性来说</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这个后排空间是充裕的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>乘坐舒适度不错，后排配置也是该有的都有</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>手工缝制的座椅可不是样子货，支撑性很到位</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>最亮眼的地方还是头枕上的“三叉戟”刺绣</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>难怪大家上车了都喜欢自拍</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200915/9f6353e55954412baf88e91fb42cdfe6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200915/7626e624d977432a900e081e15096da7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>3.0T的V6发动机</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>350马力 500牛·米</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>采埃孚8速自动变速箱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>无可挑剔的动力总成加上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>玛莎拉蒂独特的排气声浪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一脚下去</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>低音浑厚 高音亢奋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>开到马路上，仅凭声浪就能引人驻足</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200915/1dd24e91a1484d53ad5feee94e525fda.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200915/108f1e552e924fd993c89d281da26237.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200915/3ab876650f2d4fafbd25c670d87c440e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>凭借我们多年的备胎精神</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>轻轻松松就让婷姐交出了玛莎拉蒂的钥匙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不过，有句老话说的好</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>没这金刚钻就别揽瓷器活</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200915/6a5bd29862144984a22a15d2ac11b473.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200915/7cd5841fa7da430794d732530d249824.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200915/96ee121f13594493809c4caaa4664978.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200915/aa025433390a403ca6507c4f87ec7853.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200915/752deed088ed46a7a4b1eed907f5c9cb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200915/82a70594668249bc8a4fbe9a60fc24af.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200915/762181c262a2443bb49828f3deb0a85a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
